== 製作 ==
2014年6月12日，[[梦工厂动画公司|夢工廠動畫公司]]宣布預計於2016年3月18日發行這部電影，為[[汤姆·麦格拉斯|湯姆·麥葛瑞斯]]執導<ref>{{cite news|title=Dates Set for Madagascar 4, The Croods 2, Puss in Boots 2, Captain Underpants, and Hitman|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=119483|accessdate=October 15, 2014|publisher=comingsoon.net|date=June 12, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006124318/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=119483|archive-date=2014-10-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。9月30日，[[艾力·寶雲|艾力·寶雲]]與[[凱文·史貝西|凱文·史貝西]]加入了劇組，鮑德溫將飾演一個孩子，史貝西則詮釋片中的惡棍角色。12月11日，《寶貝老闆》被撤下，原本的上映日期被《[[功夫熊猫3|功夫熊貓3]]》所取代，而新的發行日期尚未公布<ref name="KFP3">{{cite news|title='Kung Fu Panda 3' Moves Out of 2015 to Avoid 'Star Wars'|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/kung-fu-panda-3-moves-756636|accessdate=December 11, 2014|newspaper=The Hollywood Reporter|date=December 11, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150103233552/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/kung-fu-panda-3-moves-756636|archive-date=2015-01-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年1月22日，電影的發布推遲到了2017年1月13日<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/dreamworks-animation-cutting-500-jobs-takes-290-million-charge-1201412212/|title=DreamWorks Animation Cutting 500 Jobs; Dawn Taubin and Mark Zoradi Exiting|work=Variety|accessdate=22 January 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161206023131/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/dreamworks-animation-cutting-500-jobs-takes-290-million-charge-1201412212/|archive-date=2016-12-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並在2015年9月再度被延至2017年3月31日，這原本是《[[內褲隊長|內褲隊長]]》的上映日期<ref name=THRShowmanPushed>{{cite news|last1=McClintock|first1=Pamela|title=Hugh Jackman's 'Greatest Showman on Earth' Pushed a Year to Christmas 2017|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/hugh-jackmans-greatest-showman-earth-824884|accessdate=September 19, 2015|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=September 18, 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160505074707/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/hugh-jackmans-greatest-showman-earth-824884|archive-date=2016-05-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。第一支官方預告片在2016年10月15日隨著《[[魔髮精靈|魔髮精靈]]》播出，幾-{天}-後，該預告片在網路上正式發布<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UQ6EGbbp_so |title=存档副本 |access-date=2016-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161022081434/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UQ6EGbbp_so |archive-date=2016-10-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
=== 評價 ===
根據[[爛蕃茄|爛蕃茄]]上收集的180篇專業影評文章，其中95篇給出了「新鮮」的正面評價，「新鮮度」為53%，[[加權平均數|平均得分]]5.50分（滿分10分）<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_boss_baby |title=The Boss Baby (2017) |website=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |accessdate=March 31, 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170401144920/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_boss_baby/ |archive-date=2017-04-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而基於另一影評網站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上的32篇評論文章，其中9篇予以好評，3篇差評，20篇褒貶不一，平均分為50（滿分100），代表「混合或中等評價」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/boss-baby|title=The Boss Baby reviews|website=Metacritic|accessdate=March 30, 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170324034249/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/boss-baby|archive-date=2017-03-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
在美國及加拿大，《寶貝老闆》與《[[攻殼機動隊_(2017年電影)|攻殼機動隊]]》一同上映，預計能在其首映週末於3,773家劇院中進帳約3,000萬美元<ref name=preview>{{cite web |url=http://www.thewrap.com/boss-baby-and-ghost-in-the-shell-to-take-on-beauty-and-the-beast-this-weekend/ |title=‘Boss Baby,’ ‘Ghost in the Shell’ to Battle ‘Beauty and the Beast’ This Weekend |date=March 29, 2017 |work=[[TheWrap|TheWrap]] |access-date=2017-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170401022741/http://www.thewrap.com/boss-baby-and-ghost-in-the-shell-to-take-on-beauty-and-the-beast-this-weekend/ |archive-date=2017-04-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。該片在星期四的午夜場上收穫150萬美元<ref>{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2017/03/ghost-in-the-shell-scarlett-johansson-boss-baby-beauty-and-the-beast-weekend-box-office-1202056616/ |title=‘Ghost In The Shell’ Collects $1.8M On Thursday Night – Box Office |accessdate=March 31, 2017 |work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170401142137/http://deadline.com/2017/03/ghost-in-the-shell-scarlett-johansson-boss-baby-beauty-and-the-beast-weekend-box-office-1202056616/ |archive-date=2017-04-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。美國首週末獲得5020萬美元的票房，位居當週票房冠軍<ref>{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2017/03/ghost-in-the-shell-scarlett-johansson-boss-baby-beauty-and-the-beast-weekend-box-office-1202056616/ |title=‘Boss Baby’ Cleans ‘Beauty And The Beast’s Clock With $51M+ Opening; ‘Ghost’ Shell-Shocked At $20M+ |accessdate=April 2, 2017 |work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170401142137/http://deadline.com/2017/03/ghost-in-the-shell-scarlett-johansson-boss-baby-beauty-and-the-beast-weekend-box-office-1202056616/ |archive-date=2017-04-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

